Class AuditFile

java.lang.Object
AuditFile
public class AuditFile extends Object
This class is responsible for storing all information from the election needed for the audit file and the election classes.
Since:
1.0

  • Method Details

    • collectFileInfo

      public void collectFileInfo()
      This function is responsible for reading through the election file and processing all of the information from it. It will store all information in the variables from this class for later use by the election classes and the audit file.
